location.fullValue: Chestnut Plan, Harrington Trails Sales Phase 2

data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in the charming Harrington Trails subdivision with close proximity to the Piney Woods elementary school built in the subdivision. This gorgeous 1 story offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an attached 2 car garage and a backyard oasis that is perfect for entertaining. Barely lived in - like NEW! It’s like getting NEW construction without the wait and high price tag! The living room and dining area have large windows to allow in lots of natural light. The kitchen features lots of storage and counter space which is sure to delight any chef! The large backyard is perfect for entertaining and get togethers and offers fur babies lots of room to explore. Don't forget the bonus storage space for all your seasonal items! The community amenities include a recreation center, splash pad, pool, walking trails and so much more! Please schedule your private tour today!
